# 3md files are Markdown with a Z axis. Without this, GitHub's language detector
# (Linguist) sees the leading-dot ASCII grids and `@plane`/`---` lines as Roff
# (troff macros start with a dot), which wrongly dominates the language bar.
*.3md linguist-language=Markdown

# The example corpus is sample content, not source - keep it out of language stats.
Examples/** linguist-documentation
docs.3md linguist-documentation
web/docs.3md linguist-documentation
web/examples-gallery.3md linguist-documentation

# Generated/vendored artifacts: don't count toward language stats.
web/gifs/** linguist-generated
web/assets/three-md.js linguist-generated
conformance/** linguist-documentation
